  "original_title": "\u0ba8\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc6\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bc0\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0ba9\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0bb2\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0bb0\u0bcb \u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0ba8\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bcb\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Litro gas supply after long days in Nuwara Eliya",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Litro gas, which was in severe shortage in the country, was supplied to the people of Nuwara Eliya today (14).",
        "Litro gas distribution stations located in the main town of Nuwara Eliya have been supplying Litro gas for more than a month, so the people have been standing in long queues since early morning to get it.",
        "The 120 liter gas containers delivered by Litro Gas Company today were delivered to the shops and all the customers who were waiting for them were not able to live up to the demand of cooking gas."
      ],
      "title_ents": [
